replies.body:
@Meddler 

Bro... why can't you change the shared exp for two champions to 75%? or just make a passive that increases shared exp for Sightstone? I don't mind the gold gap, but having to team fight mid game against a bunch of lvl 16+ champions with max ultimates while you're lvl 13~14 just hurts. 

It's christmas man, just give me that, just for testing, if turns out to be bad you can take away in January.
